Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 停下 等红绿灯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年一定会出有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会哭泣 谁又会笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:38.90,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:44.80,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:50.77,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.67,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:01:03.80,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:08.80,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:15.06,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:23.30,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:28.28,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:35.47,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:40.30,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:42.32,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:38.90,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:44.80,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:50.77,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.67,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:01:03.80,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.24,0:01:08.80,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:15.06,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:23.30,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:28.28,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:35.47,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:40.30,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:42.32,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能弄得再小了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 就这样点上火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的要点火？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收回上次说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季祭典说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你似的会说出无论如何都是朋友那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人能替代你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管怎样 我都不会破坏关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 还是挺喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真正的告白时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我朋友真好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话你可别忘了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按住他 快捆上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗 你们干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么在这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别恨我们呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫别恨你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过啦 不管怎样都不会破坏关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和高桥顺利的话就全都OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不会让你表白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有更好的办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你天真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 完事了就放开你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 小竹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他搬到化学教室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种告白时间 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放音乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始啦 告白时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那边那边 在告白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我们结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 你疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只说一次 你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都像昨天般心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 劳驾 有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 过会儿再
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 你现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在广播这帮忙 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广播
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就过去让她在那别动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在矢野去你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:06:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭我的直觉 竹内君也去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好考虑再答复
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 两个都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 刚才还在呢 哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无 无意之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没定下主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生 锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我太胆小了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没胆量打破玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的话肯定会镇定地砸烂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你天真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有我的办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那储物间的屋顶能下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是失败了 我就作鬼去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真没志气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快接
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您拨打的电话现在无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.81,0:09:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生 饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想碰碰么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰就碰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 就算打架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不想和任何人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说不想听我们的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 那就是答复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想听就面对面地说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拒绝就亲自开口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也理解一下七七的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 矢野的心情我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 知道忘记以前恋情的办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开新的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那如果是真的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的自然会成为过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的恋爱 是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吧 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真狡猾 跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你的作风呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我找不到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是最合适的 什么是最妥善的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会哭泣就能解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想也想不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再去伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再伤害任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:13:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂高桥 虽说你不想伤害别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你不想伤害的人…们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半 已经做好了受伤的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且当然 他们也不想让你痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 结果如果是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的或许是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚就这样藏起来更好些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只说一句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么最妥善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有未来的事 谁都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看结果就不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少 依赖已知的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍重自己现在的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能回到那样的日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有答案了吧 很简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不想让你痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只有这些话么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么要对我说的话么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么别的话么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧 他要撅嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也必须给出答复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的话多少我都给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会看着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会一直看着矢野你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子七美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却伤害又逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么在恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想你哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一开始就让我上火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰乱 蹂躏我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此还随便就离开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:19:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 我也喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真上火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能重写过去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那种事做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不输给过去的现在 是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在 有你在的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 还能再坚强些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我奈奈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}我几乎不知道奈奈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}之前都担心你所以没问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好告诉我你对奈奈的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在心中整理好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你 也许能继续
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.61,0:20:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能很痛苦 可我觉得有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:21:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你亲口告诉我奈奈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则就没法回到从前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事 我不知道有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 到现在也不会去面对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两年里一直是逃避过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁不能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是打算说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你顺利办成的拂晓 把它送你做礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 不是说删了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求了你多少次你不都说没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也挺天真呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会拖你后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的只是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然高桥那么认真 你也要真心相待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.06,0:22:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是改不掉闹着玩的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没资格和高桥重来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.78,0:22:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真衰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底没告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的内心我那么清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么要兜那种圈子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要还和矢野交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.51,0:22:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就会再次引起争执
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会说呢 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说会说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是对他的内心有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}那个 竹内君也一起听听奈奈的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:22:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我也听？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我人也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说其实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能不善于放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她认识在初二冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.67,0:25:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初三夏天因为事故和她死别
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.72,0:25:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.30,0:25:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 拘泥于奈奈的不是元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.98,0:25:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是高桥你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.62,0:25:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎算了吧 今天没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.31,0:25:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当是普通约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.60,0:25:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没和我爸玩儿过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.90,0:25:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:30.47,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}じゃあまたね　手を振った
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:35.76,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}後ろ姿あんなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:43.24,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕暮れの人波に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:47.93,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れながら小さくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:57.47,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたがくれた言葉を　ひとつずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:03.83,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出し 目を閉じた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:16.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せな思いだけ　ここにあるはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:24.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不安になる　どうしてなの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:30.01,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心が震えてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:35.56,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいもっとそう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:41.78,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溢れてる　この気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:49.43,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだから　好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:55.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}绝対好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:30.47,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}说声再见 我挥了挥手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:35.76,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的背影如此迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:43.24,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕阳之下 人海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:47.93,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}微微晃动渐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:57.47,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:03.83,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一字一句回忆你的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:16.66,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这里应有的 明明只是幸福的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:24.23,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可是为何心中会有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:30.01,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}原来是我心悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:35.56,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想告诉你更多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:41.78,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这满溢的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:49.43,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我喜欢你  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:55.57,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我绝对喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:07:01.96,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこにいても　どんな時も
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.87,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が消えないから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:15.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}消せない想い出として
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.96,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}受け止めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:27.32,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}時はいつか深い海で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:33.43,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}青い砂になって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:40.18,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷めない思いと一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:45.98,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:53.36,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君がいない　このベッドで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.92,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:06.61,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寝返りをうったら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:11.27,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}青空が見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:43.38,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この部屋から見える町が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:49.55,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君は好きだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:56.09,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}通り過ぎる季節が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:01.70,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:08.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}貝になって　話せなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:14.39,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君は海へ帰った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:21.36,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけど一番近くで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:26.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今日も生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:34.22,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こみあげる寂しさに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.86,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けそうな時は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:47.18,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少しだけ泣くから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:53.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこかで笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:59.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君がいない　このベッドで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:04.95,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:12.58,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}瞳をとじたら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.84,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}青空が見たら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:07:01.96,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不论何处 不论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.87,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你都不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:15.31,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我愿把它当做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.96,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不可磨灭的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:27.32,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}时间何时在深海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:33.43,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}化作青色的砂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:40.18,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与尚未冷却的思念一起
